Description: Acer Predator/Nitro performance control for Linux
 AcerControl controls Acer Predator and Nitro laptop performance profiles
 through the Linux acer_wmi platform_profile interface. It provides a
 command-line tool, a GTK4/libadwaita desktop application, an optional tray
 helper, boot-time persistence, and live thermal visibility.
